data.description: Fully updated bi-level in Northwood is ready for new owners! Brand new roof and AC in this 3 bed 1.5 bath house, along with lots of newer flooring as well. Living room upstairs and family room downstairs with extra space for whatever your needs are! Deck off dining room overlooks large backyard. Great, move-in ready home - come make it yours!
